#strong[Benchmark Reproduction Package]

The benchmark reproduction package referenced in Chapter 5 is included with this
thesis in `reproduction/benchmarks`. It contains the benchmark runner, the exported
benchmark datasets used for the evaluation, and the accompanying documentation needed
to execute the benchmark and regenerate the boxplot visualization.

The same supplementary material is available in the thesis repository at #link(
  "https://github.com/lukaskratzel/ba/tree/main/reproduction/benchmarks",
)[
  github.com/lukaskratzel/ba/tree/main/reproduction/benchmarks
].
